profile_positions.description:
FedEx Express invented express distribution and is the industry’s global leader, providing rapid, reliable, time-definite delivery to more than 220 countries and territories.

- Responsible for designing and implementing a corporate debriefing solution across Europe;
- Gathering and validation of requirements from stakeholders concerning improvements and new features to improve debriefing process;
- Customer centricity approach to ensure tailored solution to operations;
- Management of development team (8 people), providing guidance on requirements and priorities;
- Stakeholder management, presentation of debrief solution to European countries and assessment of their specific requirements, regulations and improvement outcomes.

Siemens Healthineers is a global leader in medical technology with around 50,000 employees over 70 countries. 

Working as an Industrial Engineer in order to identify  and deliver process improvements across the business.

- Identifying trends and performing statistical analysis, investigation and data collection in order to address process variation and supplier quality issues;

- Leading and facilitating Kaizen events concerning non-conformance, Internal Quality Assurance (IQA) process improvement, New Product Introduction (NPI), layout and cycle time improvement;

- Responsible for developing and maintaining of 'best-in-class' Continuous Improvement strategy;

- Delivering coaching across all functions and leading site Value Stream Mapping project in order to identify Kaizen opportunities and eliminate non-value added activities;

- Identifying and investigating process variation, performed statistical analysis and developed recommendation reports to the engineering team;

- Leading layout improvement projects in order to minimise transport and improve production flow; 

- Developing and reviewing KPIs for metric boards across departments and Kaizen process flow.

- Assisting with PFMEA and risk assessment analysis as part of a multidisciplinary group, considering the sustainability of cGMP (current Good Manufacturing Practice) and Good Documentation Practices.

- Leading and facilitating Kaizen, Workshops and projects concerning 5S and workshop re-layout, Kanban,  equipment roll out/ manufacturing readiness, line balancing, cycle time and routing.

- Certified Siemens Healthineers practitioner in the following methodologies : GROWs Coaching, Value Stream Mapping, Hoshin Kanri , Healthy Dialogues Methods, Structured Problem Solving and Agile Visual Management.
